# MedScan AI — Multimodal Clinical Document Intelligence Pipeline
## Status: ✅ APPROVED — Executing

---

## Full Architecture (3 Layers)

```
LAYER 1: INGESTION
  Scanned PDFs → Lab Reports (w/ images) → Clinical Photos → HL7/FHIR

LAYER 2: ENRICHMENT & INDEXING
  OCR Agent + Layout Parser + Table Extractor + Image Classifier
  → NER (diseases/meds/vitals) + ICD-10/SNOMED linking + Temporal normalization
  → pgvector (text) + Pinecone (image embeddings) + PostgreSQL (metadata)

LAYER 3: MULTI-AGENT QUERY (LangGraph)
  SUPERVISOR AGENT
    ├── Text RAG Agent
    ├── Table QA Agent
    └── Visual Medical Reasoning Agent
  → Safety & Hallucination Guard (citation verify + confidence + disclaimers)

LAYER 4: EVALUATION & OBSERVABILITY
  LangSmith Tracing + Custom Eval Harness + RAGAS CI
```

