## HuggingFace Task Integrations (12 Tasks)

| HF Task | Pipeline Module | Models |
|---|---|---|
| Document QA | `hf/doc_qa.py` | `impira/layoutlm-document-qa` |
| Image-to-Text | `hf/image_to_text.py` | `Salesforce/blip-image-captioning-large` |
| Image Classification | `hf/image_classification.py` | `google/vit-base-patch16-224` (fine-tuned) |
| Object Detection | `hf/object_detection.py` | `microsoft/table-transformer-detection` |
| Token Classification | `hf/token_classification.py` | `d4data/biomedical-ner-all` |
| Table QA | `hf/table_qa.py` | `google/tapas-large-finetuned-wtq` |
| Summarization | `hf/summarization.py` | `Falconsai/medical_summarization` |
| Zero-Shot Classification | `hf/zero_shot.py` | `facebook/bart-large-mnli` |
| Visual QA | `hf/vqa.py` | `Salesforce/blip-vqa-base` |
| Feature Extraction | `hf/feature_extraction.py` | `sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2` |
| Text Classification | `hf/text_classification.py` | `medicalai/ClinicalBERT` |
| OCR (Image-to-Text) | `pipeline/ocr.py` | Surya OCR + TrOCR |

